extendedInfo.description: We highlight the top business opportunities in the world. Download this free application to learn what types of small businesses and biz opps are making real money for their owners. We include such vital information as how much it costs to start a business and what type of royalty fee you will pay to the parent company. Download this free app and take control of your financial future today!
